OL,3,CComedians Jon Richardson and wife Lucy
OL,4,CBeaumont announce divorce
OL,6,FComedians Jon Richardson and Lucy
OL,7,FBeaumont have announced they are
OL,8,Fdivorcing after nine years of marriage.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the couple, who have a
OL,11,Fdaughter, said they had "jointly and
OL,12,Famicably made the difficult decision
OL,13,Fto divorce and go our separate ways".
OL,15,FThey added: "As our only priority is
OL,16,Fmanaging this difficult transition for
OL,17,Four daughter, we would ask that our
OL,18,Fprivacy is respected at this sensitive
OL,19,Ftime to protect her well-being.
OL,21,F"We will be making no further comment."
